  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of KIACTA in Preventing Renal Function Decline in AA Amyloidosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>International Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Phase 3 Study of the Efficacy and Safety of KIACTA in Preventing Renal Function Decline in Patients With AA Amyloidosis</official_title>
